TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
I can eat it for you.

Waiter! there's metallic hydrogen in my soup!

It's not a very filling soup, so lets add some more metal

 

Waiter! There's a Gaelen (kerbal from gael in galileos planet pack) in my soup!

Don't worry, it is just quality testing it for you.

Waiter, is this the soup of the day?

Well, the sun is out, so yes.

Waiter! There is not enough radiation in my Plutonium.

Told you to eat it straight away. Now it has gone cold.

Waiter, one scoop of mint soup please.

We have boiled our last Mint DVD a minute ago. Wouldn't you accept Kubuntu instead?

Waiter! Why are we asking you stupid questions?

Because your age is showing and you are getting your threads confused.

Waiter, is that a fly or a swim in my soup?

Neither! Its a walk!

waiter did the fly in their soup lose its wings to become a walk?

114710202023

No, it became a swim. Duh.

Waiter, there's a swim in my soup and a walk in my bread!

It's our All-inclusive Olympics dish.

Waiter! Something of this. And a volunteer to try it.
https://www-ochevidets-ru.translate.goog/blog/47187/?_x_tr_sch=http&_x_tr_sl=auto&_x_tr_tl=ru&_x_tr_hl=en&_x_tr_pto=wapp

Caution, photos.

You order it, then you have to eat it.

Waiter, Do you and Jebs Diner have the same Providore?

We have pomodores and humidores, sir. But we can provide what you need for additional money.

Waiter! Why is this champagne not burning?

You were supposed to eat the flame whole!

Waiter! Why is my dolphin Jebediah roast not burnt to crisp with rocket fumes?

Simple. Its fireproof dolphin. Jeb however is charred.

waiter! Theres a red button in my soup. Do i press it?

201410232023

If you want to press it, first enter the activation code in your bread.

Waiter, there's a hair in my soup.

It's part of the meal.

Waiter, what happened to the Explodium cocktail I ordered?

Im sorry sir but it exploded and took out the bartender.

waiter! There seems to be chunks of bartender in my soup.

211810232023

I think you will find those chunks of bar are actually well done and chewy.

Waiter, the soup seems happy to see me.

Oh, that's our special Emotional Support Soup. Talk to it for a while before drinking.

Waiter! My soup has flakes of... metal? they seem to be magnetic. Actually, they look like shards of hard drive platter! AAHIATESOMEALREADYGETITOUTOFME <platter shards slice through tongue> <vomit>

It's a scrapyard soup. It can eat metal plates.

5 hours ago, ColdJ said:

Waiter, the soup seems happy to see me.

Of course, it does. It's waiting already for a week.

***

Waiter! Finally, something edible for a human, please.

Sorry, we only serve cursed forum memes.

Waiter, why are you Jebediah Kerman if he was a dolphin? Is this related to my meal?

Sorry but we cannot divulge information on classified cetacean operations. Your soup is not part of this. Yet.

waiter! Theres miso in my miso soup!

153810252023

Oh good. "HEY MISO, WE FOUND YOUR FINGER!"

Waiter, Is this soup fresh?

No sir it is completely preserved. If you look at the bowl that soup was made 7654 years ago.

awsome
